<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Recuperar Senha - RS Card Store</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/login.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@700;800&family=Lato:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --color-orange-vibrant: #FF9F1C;
        }

        .login-form {
            padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center; 
            align-items: center;  
            height: 100%;         
            text-align: center;  
        }

        .icon-wrapper {
            font-size: 3.5rem; 
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--color-orange-vibrant);
        }

        .login-form h2 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .login-form p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            max-width: 350px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        }
        
        .auth-footer {
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .auth-footer .ghost-link {
            background-color: transparent;
            border: 2px solid var(--color-orange-vibrant);
            color: var(--color-orange-vibrant);
            padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .auth-footer .ghost-link:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255, 159, 28, 0.1);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .login-form {
                padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="particles-js"></div>

    <div class="auth-container" style="display: flex; width: 100%; max-width: 540px; min-height: 520px; backdrop-filter: blur(10px);">
        
        <div class="forms-container" style="position: relative; width: 100%; height: 100%;">
            <div class="login-form" style="opacity: 1; z-index: 2; transform: none;">
                
                <div class="icon-wrapper">
                    <span>ðŸ”‘</span>
                </div>

                <h2>Esqueceu sua senha?</h2>
                <p>NÃ£o se preocupe. Digite seu e-mail e enviaremos um link para vocÃª criar uma nova.</p>
                
                <% if (typeof message !== 'undefined' && message) { %>
                    <div class="success-message"><%= message %></div>
                <% } %>
                <% if (typeof errorMessage !== 'undefined' && errorMessage) { %>
                    <div class="error-message"><%= errorMessage %></div>
                <% } %>
                
                <form action="/esqueci-senha" method="POST">
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <input type="email" id="loginEmail" name="email" required placeholder=" ">
                        <label for="loginEmail">Seu E-mail de Cadastro</label>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="cta-button">Enviar Link</button>
                </form>

                <div class="auth-footer">
                    <a href="/login" class="ghost-link">Voltar para o Login</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="../js/particles.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../js/login.js"></script>
</body>
</html>